          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the potatoes are cooking, peel and finely chop your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and grate your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Trim your <strong>green beans</strong></p><p>Chop your<strong> tomato[es]</strong> roughly</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>and <strong>tomato paste </strong>in 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[200ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p>",
