    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a pot with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped shallot </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until softened</p><p>Once softened, add <strong>half </strong>the <strong>grated garlic </strong>(save the rest for later!) with your <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
