    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add a handful of <strong>flour</strong> to a plate with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Pat your <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong> dry with kitchen<strong> </strong>paper</p><p>Add the<strong> basa fillet[s]</strong> to the plate and turn several times until fully coated – this is your <strong>coated basa</strong></p>",
