    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated basa</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 6 min on each side or until golden and cooked through</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
